Привет! Это AJINIAZ QARAQALPAQ - крупней: Hello! This is AJINIAZ QARAQALPAQ - the largest chain of pharmacies in Karakalpakstan
Наша аптека впервые открылась в 2017 год: Our pharmacy first opened in 2017 under the name "AZHINIYAZ-NUKUS". Since 2019, they have been providing services under the name "AZHINIYAZ KARAKALPAK".
Название аптеки \"АЖИНИЯЗ КАРАКАЛПАК\" с: The name of the pharmacy "AZHINIYAZ KARAKALPAK" is associated with the historical novel of the Karakalpak poet Karamatdin Sultanov, written in 1971, called "AZHINIYAZ", and also with the fact that the poet named his pharmacy in honor of this novel. The poet's heirs opened their first pharmacy in 2017 under the name "AZHINIYAZ-NUKUS", and since 2019 they have been providing services under the name "AZHINIYAZ KARAKALPAK".
